{"tid":517274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美前高官：前所未有接近核戰　外交難挽","createTime":"2018-01-02T06:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T07:45:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85ed713d24ac98ca0c7151af30b83197ead7d1e0","tid":517274,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180102&d=PAKdBhU6tM4uz7DajCsFHgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=38b81742\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180102&h=95de416a\" target=\"_blank\">hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180102</a><br />\n<br />\n美前高官：前所未有接近核戰　外交難挽<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞   <br />\n       <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180102/large/a1403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180102%2Flarge%2Fa1403a.gif&h=7453ed96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n美國前參謀長聯席會議主席馬倫（Mike Mullen，圖）前日警告，美國前所未有地接近跟北韓進行核戰，他認為外交途徑解決危機機會不大。<br />\n<br />\n防長　國安顧問難阻特<br />\n<br />\n馬倫先後在喬治布殊和奧巴馬兩政府任職，他接受美國廣播公司（ABC）《本周》（This Week）節目訪問時，將現時越見緊張的局勢，歸咎於美國總統特朗普「極為破壞性」的言行。他說：「我認為我們前所未有地接近跟北韓進行核戰。」他質疑國防部長馬蒂斯、國家安全顧問麥克馬斯特及白宮幕僚長凱利能否壓得住特朗普。「他（特朗普）言出是否必行？或是我們其實可以和平解決這危機？我較傾向相信，他所說的就是他的立場，馬蒂斯、麥克馬斯特及凱利的遏制力有限。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普去年9月在聯合國大會警告，美國若要自衞或保護盟友，「除了徹底摧毀北韓，別無選擇」。8月他就矢言若北韓繼續威脅美國及其盟友，他會給北韓帶來「烈燄與怒火」。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨國會參議員格雷厄姆前日警告，若北韓試射更多導彈，將大幅增加美國先發制人的機會。<br />\n<br />\n法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t向南韓示好　有意派團參加下月平昌冬奧<br />\n國際要聞 8小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t特朗普回應核威嚇：走着瞧<br />\n國際要聞 8小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t教宗派原爆受難孩童「賀卡」<br />\n國際要聞 8小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t新年賀詞聚焦北韓核武 警告美勿玩火　金正恩：核按鈕長置辦公桌<br />\n國際要聞 8小時前"},{"pid":"d2e6c6da64da35c9bb1bc66afae0c0321127ed9e","tid":517274,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"咁幾時打呀仆街"},{"pid":"d267dbe08fa02c9ff722696af11da557a04dd033","tid":517274,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:34:36.000Z","msg":"快撚d打，冚球鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0bdec2defe462a33ae81fc5dedc18b4b875810","tid":517274,"uid":49697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78268d02b5cc9b9a996a630d4a211513c1b563ef","tid":517274,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"468a7a6cd3080b4daa2d800ca107596ae4479b08","tid":517274,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96b18f3d4f3fc883bede269599a709d9c883b882","tid":517274,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e242f84eca83e4740e48f1251b5f519c3a8ed359","tid":517274,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}